{"tid":1121702,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱女朋友上咗我屋企","createTime":"2019-04-23T13:18:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T18:15:09.000Z","uid":212061,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"118323132fe87523287c38a219bed511f40926bc","tid":1121702,"uid":212061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T13:18:56.000Z","msg":"咁一開始都係喺床一齊睇下戲<br />\n睇睇下好正常就攬下 打下茄輪咁啦<br />\n之後佢又玩下我條賓周仔<br />\n我又摷下佢咁<br />\n情到濃時我就將條賓周仔隊咗入佢塊西度<br />\n插咗幾下我先淆底 因為無戴套<br />\n所以拿拿聲抆返條賓周仔出嚟 再上返個袋<br />\n但係上返袋之後就隊唔返入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n後尾搞咗個幾鐘都唔得<br />\n雖然條女幫我用手出咗<br />\n但係都無哂mood<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n究竟點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無人試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee8f57ec3101da544c5fe9049ae0263e912e9d4c","tid":1121702,"uid":157793,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T13:21:47.000Z","msg":"你有冇叫佢拎翻賓周仔插翻你，依啲野好死，唔係你插佢就佢插你架啦"},{"pid":"f59b9e8b9c9415cc40a3f131777f8499170a9203","tid":1121702,"uid":248720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T13:26:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99241faa9bb4ea6b172820cb7f17d3866d1ec5d0","tid":1121702,"uid":212061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f59b9e8b9c9415cc40a3f131777f8499170a9203","tid":1121702,"uid":248720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T13:26:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T13:28:58.000Z","msg":"我有修剪過"},{"pid":"5efa8396105fafa8772a12fd509e92255b222ba9","tid":1121702,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T13: